## Proposed Changes

### Dataset Layer

#### [NEW] [courses.csv](file:///c:/Users/mr/OneDrive/Desktop/Arun%20project/ML%20-%20Project/dataset/courses.csv)
- 40+ rows covering 5 categories: AI, Programming, Data Science, Web Development, Cybersecurity
- Columns: `id, title, category, level, duration, rating, tags`
- Tags are comma-separated keywords used for TF-IDF vectorization

---

### ML Engine

#### [NEW] [preprocess.py](file:///c:/Users/mr/OneDrive/Desktop/Arun%20project/ML%20-%20Project/preprocess.py)
- `load_dataset()` вҖ” reads `courses.csv` with pandas, fills NaNs
- `build_feature_matrix(df)` вҖ” combines TF-IDF on `tags+category` with one-hot encoded `level` and `duration` into a single scipy sparse feature matrix

#### [NEW] [recommender.py](file:///c:/Users/mr/OneDrive/Desktop/Arun%20project/ML%20-%20Project/recommender.py)
- `build_user_vector(user_prefs, tfidf_vectorizer, feature_names)` вҖ” converts the 4 user inputs into the same vector space
- `recommend(user_prefs, top_n=5)` вҖ” main function: loads data, builds matrix, computes cosine similarity, returns top-N as list of dicts

---

### Backend API

#### [NEW] [app.py](file:///c:/Users/mr/OneDrive/Desktop/Arun%20project/ML%20-%20Project/app.py)
- `GET /` вҖ” serves `index.html`
- `GET /courses` вҖ” returns full dataset as JSON
- `POST /recommend` вҖ” accepts `{topic, level, goal, duration}` JSON, returns `[{title, category, level, rating, duration, tags}]`
- CORS enabled for local dev

#### [NEW] [requirements.txt](file:///c:/Users/mr/OneDrive/Desktop/Arun%20project/ML%20-%20Project/requirements.txt)
```
flask
flask-cors
pandas
numpy
scikit-learn
```

---

### Frontend

#### [NEW] [index.html](file:///c:/Users/mr/OneDrive/Desktop/Arun%20project/ML%20-%20Project/templates/index.html)
- Animated gradient hero header: "AI Learning Recommender"
- 4-question wizard form (dropdowns for topic, level, goal, duration)
- "Get Recommendations" button
- Results section with animated cards showing title, level, rating stars, duration badge, tags

#### [NEW] [style.css](file:///c:/Users/mr/OneDrive/Desktop/Arun%20project/ML%20-%20Project/static/css/style.css)
- Deep navy/purple dark-mode palette
- Glassmorphism cards with hover lift
- Gradient buttons with shimmer animation
- Google Font: **Inter**
- Responsive grid layout for results

#### [NEW] [app.js](file:///c:/Users/mr/OneDrive/Desktop/Arun%20project/ML%20-%20Project/static/js/app.js)
- Reads form values on button click
- `fetch("POST /recommend")` with JSON body
- Renders recommendation cards with staggered fade-in animation
- Displays loading spinner while waiting

