## Verification Plan

### Automated / Local

| Step | Command |
|------|---------|
| Install deps | `pip install -r requirements.txt` |
| Start server | `python app.py` |
| Open browser | Navigate to `http://127.0.0.1:5000` |
| API test | `curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/recommend -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d "{\"topic\":\"AI\",\"level\":\"Beginner\",\"goal\":\"Get a job\",\"duration\":\"Short\"}"` |

### Manual UI Test Cases

| Topic | Level | Goal | Duration | Expected |
|-------|-------|------|----------|---------|
| AI | Beginner | Get a job | Short | AI/ML beginner courses |
| Web Development | Intermediate | Improve skills | Medium | Mid-level web dev courses |
| Cybersecurity | Advanced | Academic learning | Long | Advanced security content |
| Data Science | Beginner | Academic learning | Short | Intro data science |
| Programming | Intermediate | Get a job | Medium | Python/Java career tracks |

### Deployment (Optional)
- Push to GitHub вҶ’ connect to **Render** (free tier) вҶ’ set start command to `gunicorn app:app`
